# Fluxbox key bindings
# Written by Amthrax
#
# Mod1 = Alt, Mod4 = Flag

Control Escape :RootMenu

# Window switching
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow

# Tab switching
Control Tab :NextTab
Control Shift Tab :PrevTab

# Window moving
Control Mod1 Shift Up :MoveUp 10
Control Mod1 Shift Down :MoveDown 10
Control Mod1 Shift Left :MoveLeft 10
Control Mod1 Shift Right :MoveRight 10

# Window sizing/layout
Control Mod1 Up :Raise
Control Mod1 Down :MaximizeVertical
Control Mod1 Left :MaximizeWindow
Control Mod1 Right :MaximizeHorizontal

# Window properties
Mod1 F1 :Minimize
Mod1 F2 :ShadeWindow
Mod1 F3 :ToggleDecor
Mod1 F4 :Close

# Workspace switching
Mod4 Left :PrevWorkspace
Mod4 Right :NextWorkspace
Mod4 F1 :Workspace 1
Mod4 F2 :Workspace 2
Mod4 F3 :Workspace 3
Mod4 F4 :Workspace 4
Mod4 F5 :Workspace 5
Mod4 F6 :Workspace 6
Mod4 F7 :Workspace 7
Mod4 F8 :Workspace 8
Mod4 F9 :Workspace 9
Mod4 F10 :Workspace 10
Mod4 F11 :Workspace 11
Mod4 F12 :Workspace 12

# Program hotkeys
Control Mod1 E :ExecCommand emacs
Control Mod1 D :ExecCommand Eterm
Control Mod1 F :ExecCommand firefox
